#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:1
msgid "KV Cache CPU Offload Guide"
msgstr "KV缓存CPU卸载指南"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:3
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:5
msgid ""
"KV Cache CPU Offload enables offloading inactive KV cache blocks from NPU"
" memory to CPU memory, allowing vLLM to handle longer contexts or more "
"concurrent requests when NPU memory is limited. When a prefix cache miss "
"occurs on the NPU but the data exists in CPU memory, the KV cache is "
"asynchronously loaded back to the NPU, reducing recomputation latency."
msgstr ""
"KV缓存CPU卸载功能可将非活跃的KV缓存块从NPU内存卸载到CPU内存，使vLLM在NPU内存受限时能够处理更长的上下文或更多并发请求。当NPU上发生前缀缓存未命中但数据存在于CPU内存时，KV缓存会被异步加载回NPU，从而减少重计算延迟。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:7
msgid ""
"This feature is built on vLLM's `OffloadingConnector` framework and "
"provides an Ascend NPU-specific implementation (`NPUOffloadingSpec`) that"
" uses dedicated NPU streams for efficient asynchronous data transfers "
"between NPU and CPU."
msgstr ""
"该功能基于vLLM的`OffloadingConnector`框架构建，并提供了Ascend NPU专用实现（`NPUOffloadingSpec`），使用专用NPU流在NPU和CPU之间进行高效的异步数据传输。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:9
msgid "Key Concepts"
msgstr "关键概念"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:11
msgid ""
"**CPU Block Pool**: A pre-allocated pool of CPU memory blocks (optionally"
" pinned) used to store offloaded KV cache data."
msgstr ""
"**CPU块池**：预分配的CPU内存块池（可选锁定），用于存储卸载的KV缓存数据。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:12
msgid ""
"**Asynchronous Transfer**: NPU-to-CPU (D2H) and CPU-to-NPU (H2D) "
"transfers are performed on separate NPU streams, overlapping with "
"computation to minimize latency impact."
msgstr ""
"**异步传输**：NPU到CPU（D2H）和CPU到NPU（H2D）传输在独立的NPU流上执行，与计算重叠以最小化延迟影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:13
msgid ""
"**LRU Eviction**: The CPU-side block pool uses an LRU (Least Recently "
"Used) eviction policy to manage limited CPU memory efficiently."
msgstr ""
"**LRU淘汰**：CPU端块池使用LRU（最近最少使用）淘汰策略来高效管理有限的CPU内存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:15
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "使用方法"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:17
msgid "Python API"
msgstr "Python API"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:47
msgid "Online Serving"
msgstr "在线服务"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:64
msgid "Configuration Parameters"
msgstr "配置参数"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:66
msgid "`kv_connector`: Must be set to `\"OffloadingConnector\"`."
msgstr "`kv_connector`：必须设置为`\"OffloadingConnector\"`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:67
msgid ""
"`kv_role`: Set to `\"kv_both\"` to enable both storing and loading of KV "
"cache."
msgstr ""
"`kv_role`：设置为`\"kv_both\"`以同时启用KV缓存的存储和加载。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:68
msgid ""
"`num_cpu_blocks`: Number of blocks to allocate in CPU memory. Increase "
"this value for longer context scenarios. Each block consumes memory "
"proportional to `block_size × num_layers × (key_size + value_size)`."
msgstr ""
"`num_cpu_blocks`：在CPU内存中分配的块数。对于更长上下文场景，请增加此值。每个块消耗的内存与`block_size × num_layers × (key_size + value_size)`成正比。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:69
msgid ""
"`block_size`: The CPU-side block size. Should be a multiple of the NPU-"
"side block size. Typical value: `128`."
msgstr ""
"`block_size`：CPU端块大小。应为NPU端块大小的倍数。典型值：`128`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:70
msgid "`spec_name`: Must be `\"NPUOffloadingSpec\"` for Ascend NPU."
msgstr "`spec_name`：对于Ascend NPU，必须为`\"NPUOffloadingSpec\"`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:71
msgid "`spec_module_path`: Must be `\"vllm_ascend.kv_offload.npu\"`."
msgstr "`spec_module_path`：必须为`\"vllm_ascend.kv_offload.npu\"`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:73
msgid "How It Works"
msgstr "工作原理"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:75
msgid ""
"**Normal inference**: KV cache blocks are computed and stored on the NPU "
"as usual."
msgstr ""
"**正常推理**：KV缓存块照常在NPU上计算和存储。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:76
msgid ""
"**Eviction to CPU**: When NPU memory is full and new blocks are needed, "
"inactive KV cache blocks are asynchronously copied to CPU memory via a "
"dedicated D2H NPU stream."
msgstr ""
"**卸载到CPU**：当NPU内存已满且需要新块时，非活跃的KV缓存块通过专用D2H NPU流异步复制到CPU内存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:77
msgid ""
"**Prefix cache hit (CPU)**: When a request shares a prefix with "
"previously computed data, and the prefix cache is not found on NPU but "
"exists in CPU memory, the KV cache blocks are asynchronously loaded back "
"from CPU to NPU via a dedicated H2D NPU stream."
msgstr ""
"**前缀缓存命中（CPU）**：当请求与先前计算的数据共享前缀，且NPU上未找到前缀缓存但CPU内存中存在时，KV缓存块通过专用H2D NPU流从CPU异步加载回NPU。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:78
msgid ""
"**LRU management**: The CPU block pool uses LRU eviction to discard the "
"least recently used blocks when CPU memory is full."
msgstr ""
"**LRU管理**：当CPU内存已满时，CPU块池使用LRU淘汰策略丢弃最近最少使用的块。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:80
msgid "Optional: KV Cache Events"
msgstr "可选：KV缓存事件"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:82
msgid ""
"You can enable KV cache event publishing for monitoring or debugging "
"purposes:"
msgstr ""
"您可以启用KV缓存事件发布以进行监控或调试："

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:102
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "注意事项"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:104
msgid "This feature requires vLLM v1 engine."
msgstr "此功能需要vLLM v1引擎。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:105
msgid ""
"Adjust `num_cpu_blocks` based on available CPU memory. Using too many "
"blocks may cause out-of-memory errors on the host."
msgstr ""
"根据可用CPU内存调整`num_cpu_blocks`。使用过多块可能导致主机内存不足错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:106
msgid ""
"Pinned (page-locked) memory is used when available for optimal transfer "
"performance."
msgstr ""
"在可用时使用锁定（页锁定）内存以获得最佳传输性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:107
msgid ""
"The `gpu_memory_utilization` parameter controls how much NPU memory is "
"reserved for KV cache. Lower values leave less NPU memory for KV cache, "
"making offloading more active."
msgstr ""
"`gpu_memory_utilization`参数控制为KV缓存保留的NPU内存量。较低的值会为KV缓存留下较少的NPU内存，使卸载更加活跃。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/feature_guide/kv_cache_cpu_offload.md:108
msgid ""
"For production workloads, benchmark with realistic request patterns to "
"find the optimal `num_cpu_blocks` and `block_size` settings."
msgstr ""
"对于生产工作负载，请使用真实请求模式进行基准测试，以找到最佳的`num_cpu_blocks`和`block_size`设置。"